Niue Documentation


	SHORTCUTS


Here's an overview of the most common shortcuts:

	FILE:

ctrl-N			New Window
ctrl-shift-N		New Project
ctrl-O			Open Project
ctrl-B			Browse Projects

ctrl-S			Save
ctrl-shift-S		Save-As


	EDIT:

ctrl-Z			Undo
ctrl-X			Cut
ctrl-C			Copy
ctrl-V			Paste

ctrl-A			Select All
ctrl-shift-A		Deselect All

ctrl-]			Indent
ctrl-[			Undent
ctrl-shift-[		Quote
ctrl-shift-]		Unquote


	SEARCH:

ctrl-shift-F		Search Multiple Docs

ctrl-F			Find
ctrl-G			Find Forward
ctrl-D			Find Backward
ctrl-H			Find Selection
ctrl-J			Replace Selection

ctrl-,			Go To Line


	PROJECT:

ctrl-T			Add Files To Project
ctrl-Y			Build Rules

ctrl-M		Make
ctrl-U			Make Clean
ctrl-R			Run

ctrl-shift-E		Make Backup
ctrl-shift-E		Export App		
		

	VIEW:

ctrl-9			Switch File Up
ctrl-0			Switch File Down

